/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲最撚煩<br />\n最雞肋<br />\n用又唔係用唔到，但要mon住佢充成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我一直都係用原裝同verbatim，你呢啲幾蚊條冇mfi晶片既我真係睇唔上眼，錢事小，爆炸著火燒屋問題先大</blockquote>"},{"pid":"261e32a97b6381bedcbe622797e9c26b0498e9cf","tid":1192162,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"IKEA<br />\n但成日無貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4492abb6869a0c655d339185f1edcee8242f9369","tid":1192162,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f19dc6085e1b479c8bd793b99742c74c4e1bb9e","tid":1192162,"uid":118647,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b1d198f6ca2f32406270fdd1b0c94c70f038554","tid":1192162,"uid":92500,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"f9c3f29227270e503d27747939bd43d802cc4435","tid":1192162,"uid":118647,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"用呢啲線等半年後燒底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"我一直都係用原裝同verbatim，你呢啲幾蚊條冇mfi晶片既我真係睇唔上眼，錢事小，爆炸著火燒屋問題係大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"最撚基本真係要mfi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c4ef7dac68b5e70c6fe5a2195bcb7f4b82d0e1","tid":1192162,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4492abb6869a0c655d339185f1edcee8242f9369","tid":1192162,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor